.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: blue, green, red, white, yellow
Nationality: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
House: cottage, townhouse, palace, tower, modern
Cigar: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
Food: lemon, onion, strawberry, lime, eggplant
1. Nationality:british == Color:red
2. Nationality:swedish == Food:strawberry
3. Nationality:danish == House:tower
4. Color:green is on the left of Color:white
5. Color:green == House:townhouse
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Food:onion
7. Color:yellow == Cigar:dunhill
8. House:palace is in the middle
9. Nationality:norwegian is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Food:lemon
11. Food:eggplants is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:bluemaster == House:cottage
13. Nationality:german == Cigar:prince
14. Nationality:norwegian is on the left or right of Color:blue
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of House:modern

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Food		|     lemon	|    eggplant	|     onion	|     lime	|      strawberry	|
| House	|    modern	|     tower	|     palace	|    townhouse	|      cottage	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   bluemaster	|
